The paper is about text matching, which is a core problem in natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions information retrieval (IR), which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The use of deep learning technology suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.LG (Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
